{"type":"text","timestamp":1775872526970,"sessionID":"ses_285c15d52ffepfa12E8jzO5MFc","part":{"id":"prt_d7a3fe3cb001l2HcTSawbQXQtI","messageID":"msg_d7a3fd6ac001t4rzfwLyCWL7xc","sessionID":"ses_285c15d52ffepfa12E8jzO5MFc","type":"text","text":"## Verification Report for AR-022 — CLI publish command\n\n### Status: **FAIL** - Multiple critical gaps and test failures\n\n### Summary of Issues\n\n#### **1. Missing Commands (Critical)**\n- ❌ `invoke` command not implemented in `agentcube/cli/main.py`\n- ❌ `status` command not implemented in `agentcube/cli/main.py`\n- The spec defines 5 commands: pack, build, publish, invoke, status. Only 3 are implemented.\n\n#### **2. Missing Runtime Classes (Critical)**\n- ❌ `InvokeRuntime` class not implemented (missing file: `agentcube/runtime/invoke_runtime.py`)\n- ❌ `StatusRuntime` class not implemented (missing file: `agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py`)\n- These are core runtime classes required by the spec\n\n#### **3. Missing Package Structure (Critical)**\n- ❌ `agentcube/operations/__init__.py` not present\n- Spec explicitly requires this placeholder module\n\n#### **4. Test Failures (13 failed, 157 passed)**\nKey failures:\n- Validation tests failing (language, build_mode, port validators not working with `model_construct`)\n- Namespace creation tests failing\n- Version flag test failing (`SystemExit(2)` instead of success)\n- Patch existing deployment/service tests failing\n- CRD not found handling tests failing\n\n#### **5. Package Configuration Mismatches**\n\n**pyproject.toml:**\n- ❌ `requires-python = \">=3.9\"` (spec requires `>=3.10`)\n- ❌ Missing dependencies: `httpx>=0.24.0`, `packaging>=23.0`, `importlib-resources>=6.0.0`, `semver>=3.0.0`\n- ❌ Missing test dependencies: `pytest-asyncio>=0.21.0`, `httpx-mock>=0.10.0`\n- ❌ Missing k8s optional dependency: `kubernetes>=28.0.0` in optional-deps\n\n#### **6. Typer App Configuration Mismatch**\n- ❌ Spec: `Typer(name=\"agentcube\", no_args_is_help=True, rich_markup_mode=\"rich\", add_completion=False)`\n- ❌ Implementation: Only `Typer(help=\"AgentCube CLI...\")` - missing all other parameters\n\n#### **7. Package Exports Mismatch**\n**agentcube/__init__.py:**\n- ❌ Missing `__author__ = \"AgentCube Community\"`\n- ❌ Missing `__email__ = \"agentcube@volcano.sh\"`\n- ❌ Export list includes `MetadataOptions` (not in spec's `__all__`)\n- Spec exports: `[\"app\", \"PackRuntime\", \"BuildRuntime\", \"PublishRuntime\", \"InvokeRuntime\"]`\n- Actual exports: `[\"__version__\", \"app\", \"PackRuntime\", \"BuildRuntime\", \"PublishRuntime\", \"MetadataOptions\"]`\n\n#### **8. Version Callback Implementation Mismatch**\n- ❌ Spec defines separate `version_callback` function\n- ❌ Implementation embeds version handling in `main` callback\n\n#### **9. AgentMetadata Field Defaults Mismatch**\n- ❌ Spec: `description`, `version`, `region`, `registry_url`, `registry_username`, `registry_password` should be `Optional[str]` with `None` default\n- ❌ Implementation: Uses empty string `\"\"` defaults (not truly optional)\n- ❌ Spec: `image`, `auth`, `k8s_deployment` should be `Optional[Dict[str, Any]]` with `None` default\n- ❌ Implementation: Uses `default_factory=dict` (always initialized)\n\n#### **10. Publish Command Parameter Mismatch**\n**Main.py publish command:**\n- ✅ Most parameters match spec\n- ❌ Extra parameters: `workload_manager_url`, `router_url` (not in spec's publish signature)\n- These should come from metadata, not CLI options per spec\n\n### Positive Findings\n\n✅ **Correct implementations:**\n- Package layout structure mostly matches (except missing items)\n- Console script entry point matches: `kubectl-agentcube = \"agentcube.cli.main:app\"`\n- Pack and build commands signature match spec\n- PublishRuntime class structure matches spec\n- PackRuntime, BuildRuntime, DockerService, MetadataService, KubernetesProvider, AgentCubeProvider classes present\n- MetadataOptions dataclass fields match spec\n- CR API constants match: group=\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", version=\"v1alpha1\", plural=\"agentruntimes\"\n\n### Recommendations\n\n**Critical fixes needed:**\n1. Implement missing `invoke` and `status` commands\n2. Create `InvokeRuntime` and `StatusRuntime` classes\n3. Create `agentcube/operations/__init__.py` placeholder\n4. Fix pyproject.toml dependencies and Python version\n5. Fix Typer app initialization parameters\n6. Fix AgentMetadata optional field defaults\n7. Fix failing tests (especially validation and namespace tests)\n8. Remove extra CLI parameters from publish command (workload_manager_url, router_url)\n9. Add missing exports to `__all__` and package metadata fields","time":{"start":1775872526967,"end":1775872526967}}}
